OL,3,CMan who dismembered wife had tortured
OL,4,Cand killed a puppy
OL,6,FThe family of a woman whose husband
OL,7,Fkilled her pets before murdering her
OL,8,Fhave called for a national register of
OL,9,Fanimal abusers.
OL,11,FHolly Bramley, who was 26, was stabbed
OL,12,Fto death and dismembered by her
OL,13,Fabusive husband at their flat in
OL,14,FLincoln in March last year. Her
OL,15,Fremains were dumped in a river.
OL,17,FHer killer, 28-year-old Nicholas
OL,18,FMetson, had previously tortured and
OL,19,Fkilled her pets.
