OL,3,CMan who dismembered wife had tortured
OL,4,Cand killed a puppy
OL,6,FHer mother, Annette Bramley, said on
OL,7,Fone occasion Metson put their puppy in
OL,8,Fthe washing machine.
OL,10,FShe told ITV News: "Holly managed to
OL,11,Fstop the cycle of the machine and get
OL,12,Fthe puppy out but then he drowned the
OL,13,Fpuppy in the bath.
OL,15,F"We were fearful for Holly's life
OL,16,Fafter that and I expressed those
OL,17,Fconcerns to the police some years ago.
OL,18,FI always thought Holly would be his
OL,19,Ffirst human victim.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
