OL,6,F"I can just see her now with that
OL,7,Flittle smile on her face thinking
OL,8,Fpeople can see that I'm a person not
OL,9,Fjust a victim, that I did exist and
OL,10,Feverybody now knows who I am and I'm
OL,11,Fhelping others."
OL,13,FHolly's sister, Sarah Jayne Lindop,
OL,14,Fsaid: "On hearing that initial news
OL,15,Fthat something awful had happened to
OL,16,FHolly, I instantly knew it was him.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
