OL,6,F"Coercion is engrained, it's deep. It
OL,7,Fwould have been impossible for her to
OL,8,Fleave knowing what he has done and
OL,9,Fwhat he could do - if there were still
OL,10,Fanimals within the home. I just can't
OL,11,Fimagine the fear she would've felt."
OL,13,FHolly's family have now launched a
OL,14,Fpetition to create a national register
OL,15,Fof animal abusers, named 'Holly's Law'.
OL,17,FAnnette said: "Had there been a way of
OL,18,FHolly or anyone really being able to
OL,19,Ffind out the previous history of
OL,20,Fsomeone and their abuse of animals it
OL,21,Fwould be a red flag to them."
