OL,6,FSarah Jayne added: "I think the impact
OL,7,Fcould be absolutely huge. If police
OL,8,Fare called to a domestic situation and
OL,9,Fthey are able to search for a history
OL,10,Fof animal abuse then that will raise
OL,11,Fthe risk for that victim."
OL,13,FThere is a well-documented link
OL,14,Fbetween animal cruelty and violence
OL,15,Ftowards people and some studies
OL,16,Fsuggest that abuse of pets or the
OL,17,Fthreat of it is not uncommon in
OL,18,Fdomestic abuse cases.
