OL,6,FDr Gerri Moxon, a clinical
OL,7,Fpsychologist, said: "It's about
OL,8,Fdominance, it's about power, and
OL,9,Fcreating a real threat.
OL,11,F"There's a real awareness that if a
OL,12,Fperson is aware of that, to an animal
OL,13,Fso vulnerable, it creates a real sense
OL,14,Fof threat and fear to the individual
OL,15,Fin the relationship of what they might
OL,16,Fdo to them."
